name: Glitch Worshiper
description: 1  The dominant, continuing search for a noiseless channel has been – and will always be – no more than a regrettable, ill-fated dogma.  Acknowledge that although the constant search for complete transparency brings newer,‘better’ media, every one of these improved techniques will always possess their own inherentfingerprints of imperfection.  Glitch Studies Manifesto, Rosa Menkman
